#!/usr/bin/env testml


*jsc.validate(*json) == *valid


=== Test 1 - format: uri-template - a valid uri-template
--- valid: true
--- jsc
{"format": "uri-template"}
--- json
"http://example.com/dictionary/{term:1}/{term}"


=== Test 2 - format: uri-template - an invalid uri-template
--- valid: false
--- ^jsc
--- json
"http://example.com/dictionary/{term:1}/{term"


=== Test 3 - format: uri-template - a valid uri-template without variables
--- valid: true
--- ^jsc
--- json
"http://example.com/dictionary"


=== Test 4 - format: uri-template - a valid relative uri-template
--- valid: true
--- ^jsc
--- json
"dictionary/{term:1}/{term}"


